text: Portlaoise RFC is an Irish rugby team based in Portlaoise, Leinster, playing in Division 1B of the Leinster League. The club is based just off the N77 in Togher, near the M7 interchange. ==References== * Category:Irish rugby union teams Category:Rugby clubs established in 1966 Category:Rugby union clubs in County Laois Category:Sport in Portlaoise
